summary:
Past, Present and Future. 

I have been working since I was 16 in a variety of jobs, from Hospitality, Fashion, Sales, Telecommunications, Coaching, Business Development, and Events. In 2013, to achieve my dream I moved to London to work on my loved one: music. Since then, I couldn't be more proud of how much I have learned and grown, as a professional and person. 

I can fastly adapt and build on my essential skills whilst rapidly gaining others. One of my strengths is the ability to connect with people and build long-lasting relationships with clients and colleagues alike. I am reliable, proactive, highly organised, time-sensitive, sincere, funny, determined, tenacious, and very passionate about music, football, great food, learning, and getting things done. I am always striving for excellence. In everything.
